{"tid":1971754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭提名　罪犯做上法官　頒佈連登禁制令","createTime":"2020-04-14T06:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T15:44:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8234fdb028e71d57feb0d236cb7e11c62e065e01","tid":1971754,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:34:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2676368002599274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2676368002599274&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=f28f2cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2676368002599274</a><br />\n<br />\nColeman the Filth 禁言禁制令黑手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/io5khxL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fio5khxL.jpg&h=56b06959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2916209465078001/permalink/3161804937185118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2916209465078001%2Fpermalink%2F3161804937185118%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=3b22278b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2916209465078001/permalink/3161804937185118/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6z9QEvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6z9QEvL.jpg&h=33a90e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭杏家:<br />\n#原來有刑事犯罪記錄可以做法官<br />\n<br />\nColin Yau:<br />\n有刑事案底還可以擔任法律業界之職？原則上應該不可能的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699414016961339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699414016961339&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e901287b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699414016961339</a><br />\n<br />\n三尖八角嘅法官Coleman（古怪藝名：高浩文），20年前請咗個男性外傭做黑工看更，被輕判罰款之後（近年嘅量刑標準係要坐幾個月監）仲冇申報比公會，又多條專業失德。<br />\n<br />\n跟住就開始生意失敗，後來比佢搵到條水路，就係家事法。喺佢同同業、垃圾法改會嘅慫恿之下，法庭獲得更多權力去控制撫養地位。好壞我不置評，但肯定冇民主授權。因為係跟英國，所以佢又可以扮專家。後來塘水滾滾吓就變成家事法庭法官。<br />\n<br />\n跟住幫政府擋刀嘅法改會搞「檔案法」，佢又叉隻腳埋去。然後就扶搖直上。去到high court唔夠一年，就收order搞開始禁言令。比國際組織互聯網協會加入反對禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n篇所謂判詞，有一半篇幅擦鞋引用馬道立，同垃圾政治演說，完全無視一切法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699420316960709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699420316960709&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=2bb07a58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699420316960709</a><br />\n<br />\n法律界 #無產階級翻身系列<br />\n<br />\n原來除咗律政司告票文員仔免學費免學師做大律師、裁判官，<br />\n<br />\n請黑工加專業失德嘅罪犯都可以做高院法官，仲重整埋啲鎮壓示威、言論自由嘅禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699427756959965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699427756959965&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=6b4cb749\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699427756959965</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;高浩文法官特意表示要用引號括著「示威者」三字，以免顯得他們的暴行可視為正當。他更直呼示威者「罪犯」，重申法治不能以不斷犯法來維護。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n原來佢先係罪犯，99年請黑工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699423343627073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699423343627073&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=8f1cc9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699423343627073</a><br />\n<br />\n搵個鬼佬出嚟做極端、單方面、破壞權利與自由嘅判決，愚夫愚婦都以為係香嘅。含係逆向種族歧視，唔含就屈你種族歧視。最神奇嘅twist係：條鬼佬原來係罪犯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699526926950048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699526926950048&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=3c719280\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699526926950048</a><br />\n<br />\n起底禁制令實際上係寒禁（chill）針對政府嘅私人刑事調查。一個罪犯做上法官，就禁止人調查犯罪，真係好佛洛伊德。 ĐɆɆ₱Ɇ₴₮ ₣Ɇ₳Ɽ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699537840282290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2699537840282290&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=a9b21c6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2699537840282290</a><br />\n<br />\n之前我仲以為嗰份垃圾判詞寫乜春「你話寒蟬效應？我話見到示威者打異見仲心寒呀。」純粹垃圾修辭撚「寒」字。原來個罪犯法官堅心寒，佢就係制度不公而執返身彩嘅罪犯，懼怕私刑正義。"},{"pid":"b09c30dfd618391b5423706a1c8d4e54664d54e5","tid":1971754,"uid":49781,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"香港法治世紀笑話<br />\nForward埋去外國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418393c260a51ca4b509e4e74436087a03b52c46","tid":1971754,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"禁兒登屎屎台就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41948eb941dfc4b833b6a318dbb6f2a8fc70fd1","tid":1971754,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"正宗white trash"},{"pid":"f3ed14b9c91eed731fe19dde06a9a25ba2d21958","tid":1971754,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"418393c260a51ca4b509e4e74436087a03b52c46","tid":1971754,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"禁兒登屎屎台就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"禁到既話你估佢唔想禁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb222a71cbdde601dcd42b7b1bd1ac49ac823a05","tid":1971754,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0